Formed in the unholy union between a newly ordained Drow high priestess and a powerful Tanar'ri, a Draegloth is a half Fiend terror that stalks the Underdark. While half-fiends of all varieties are not as rare as one might hope, Draegloth are perhaps the only variety that is regularly, intentionally, even ritually created by a mortal race. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Champions of Ruin